.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lauryn-hill@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lauryn-hill@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lauryn-hill@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauryn-hill">Lauryn Hill</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fugees">Fugees</a>已确认他们计划于今年晚些时候进行的欧洲和英国巡演将按计划进行，并就他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lauryn-hill-and-the-fugees-have-quietly-cancelled-their-us-tour-3781582">最近取消的北美巡演</a>发表了评论。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="351" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/why-the-score-is-one-of-the-greatest-hip-hop-albums-ever-774792"><b>为什么《The Score》是有史以来最伟大的嘻哈专辑之一</b></a></li></ul><p>昨天（8月7日），据透露，希尔与逃亡者乐队的北美演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lauryn-hill-and-the-fugees-have-quietly-cancelled-their-us-tour-3781582">在原定的徒步旅行开始前三天</a>被取消。当时，没有透露取消的理由或解释，英国和欧洲巡演的命运悬而未决。</p><p>现在，希尔澄清了情况，首先在社交媒体上确认欧洲和英国巡演仍在进行—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lauryn-hill-and-the-fugees-add-more-dates-to-2024-uk-and-european-miseducation-anniversary-tour-3778879">他们上周刚刚宣布了欧洲巡演的额外演出</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768385" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768385" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768385" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_laurenhill_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768385" class="wp-caption-text"> 4 月 21 日，Fugees 乐队主唱 Lauryn Hill 在印第安纳州科切拉谷音乐艺术节期间登台表演 图片来源：Scott Dudelson/Getty Images for Coachella</figcaption></figure><p>希尔在 Instagram 上写道：“英国和欧洲的演出正在按计划进行。”</p><p>然后她继续解释了北美巡演被取消的原因：“去年，我受伤了，需要重新安排我的一些演出。遗憾的是，一些媒体对耸人听闻和标题党的偏爱似乎创造了一种叙事，影响了巡演北美部分的门票销售。我对自己的意图和对艺术的承诺的信任和信念似乎被这种不幸的描绘所掩盖。”</p><p>她在帖子的最后向北美粉丝保证，一旦“这些不可预见的情况得到解决”，他们将“全力回归”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-YhQNQOjld/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></di